{"type": "article", "id": 28059, "title": "男士洗浴袋", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-12T06:57:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021528022Flc6S5wEpaPKsIB.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>出门旅游，打包洗浴用品或许是不少人都会纠结的一件事：普通的收纳袋很有可能在经历长途颠簸后把东西弄得一团乱，让你在需要的时候不得不在袋子里掏来掏去。Tashtego 是一款专门为男性设计的洗浴袋，内部有着数个分隔开的小袋子，刚好可以容纳每一件常用的洗浴用品。把袋子的上半部分翻下，卷起后用皮带系紧不仅可以确保每一件物品都固定不动，也防止了物品接触后造成污染。Tashtego 由防水的打蜡棉帆布制成，如果需要清洁，只要用水管将污渍冲洗掉即可。目前它正在 Kickstarter 上<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1292087458/tashtego-the-roll-up-travel-kit-to-tame-your-toile\">开展众筹</a>，最低价为 35 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152758a5OhQlvUeWRVT1Em.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152800KPX3URDbZtfl8AJi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60923077\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021528007gUbPGsDFJVnxj0T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152801UWkPSVay0i8O7ueT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}